<HEAD>President Proposes Ban on PAC Campaign Contributions</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: Subs last graf pvs to CORRECT that prohibition applies to earned
outside income, sted all outside income; subs 4th graf pvs, Suggesting
a, with precise figure; inserts 2 grafs after 6th graf pvs, ``PACs weaken,
